ParkSense Admin Dashboard

Manage Your Smart Parking System with Rover Technology

Welcome to ParkSense

ParkSense revolutionizes parking management with our autonomous rover technology. Our rover navigates parking lots to monitor occupancy, detect vehicles, and optimize space allocation in real-time. Integrated with advanced sensors and AI, it ensures seamless parking operations, reduces congestion, and enhances user experience.

Why ParkSense?

Autonomous Rover

Our rover autonomously patrols the parking lot, using cameras and sensors to detect vehicle number plates and measure distances, ensuring accurate occupancy data.

Real-Time Monitoring

Get instant updates on parking slot availability, vehicle entries, and exits through our intuitive dashboard, powered by real-time data from the rover.

Smart Allocation

The system intelligently assigns slots based on vehicle size and proximity, optimizing space usage and reducing search time for drivers.
